            <subsection name="Overview">
                <p>
                    This section gives a short overview on the used technologies
                    in the basic, medium and advanced sample.
                    This should not be mistaken with a tutorial to the according technologies! The purpose of the technology section is, to get a brief idea why a specific technology is used and what the general usage patterns are. Additional references are provided to get detailed information.
                </p>  
                   
               <p>
            We recommend to start reading with the example documentation, then start reading the code to get an initial overview on the example application and follow up in this section to get an in-depth understanding of technologies and patterns. Eventually go back into the sources and try to understand the details of the implementations.
            </p>
                
